abstract = {Technologies nowadays are booming. Artificial intelligence has been in every aspect of society, including education. Undergraduate innovation practice education is fundamental for talent fostering. Artificial intelligence has introduced unexpected reforms for the ground. Our work targets on the application of artificial intelligence in university students' innovation practice education. Edges and challenges are brought up with relevant suggestions. Literature review and case analysis help explain its application in aspects like personalized learning and smart tutoring. Implications on students' innovative ability, learning efficiency, education quality, and the way to quickly and effectively apply artificial intelligence in universities have also been investigated.},
